{"kanda":6,"sarga":44,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"युध्यतामेनतेषांतुतदावानरराक्षसाम् ।रविरस्तंगतोरात्रिःप्रवृत्ताप्राणहारिणी","trans":"Thus, as the Vanaras and Rakshasas were battling, the Sun began to set, which is not favourable to the life of Vanaras.","words":[{"d":"तेषाम्","m":"their"},{"d":"वानररक्षसाम्","m":"Vanara and Rakshasa"},{"d":"युध्यतामेव","m":"battling"},{"d":"तदा","m":"then"},{"d":"रविः","m":"sun"},{"d":"अस्तम्","m":"set"},{"d":"गतः","m":"went"},{"d":"प्राणहारिणी","m":"harmful to the life"},{"d":"रात्रिः","m":"night"},{"d":"प्रवृत्ता","m":"began."}]},{"v":2,"dev":"अन्योन्यंबद्धवैराणांघोराणांजयमिच्छताम् ।सम्प्रवृत्तंनिशायुद्धंतदावानररक्षसाम्","trans":"Then Vanaras and dreadful Rakshasas being strongly inimical to each other started the night battle wishing victory.","words":[{"d":"तदा","m":"then"},{"d":"अन्योन्यम्","m":"to one another"},{"d":"बद्धवैराणाम्","m":"strong enmity"},{"d":"घोराणाम्","m":"dreadful"},{"d":"जयम्","m":"victory"},{"d":"इच्छताम्","m":"wishing"},{"d":"वानररक्षसाम्","m":"Vanara and Rakshasas"},{"d":"निशायुद्धम्","m":"night battle"},{"d":"सम्प्रवृत्तम्","m":"started."}]},{"v":3,"dev":"राक्षसोऽसीतिहरयोहरिश्चाऽसीतिराक्षसाः ।अन्योन्यंसमरेजघ्नुस्तस्मिंस्तमसिदारुणे","trans":"In the fierce darkness that prevailed, monkeys hit monkeys thinking to be Rakshasas and Rakshasas hit Rakshasas thinking to be Vanaras (not knowing in darkness) hit each other.","words":[{"d":"दारुणे","m":"fierce"},{"d":"तस्मिन्","m":"them"},{"d":"तमसि","m":"darkness"},{"d":"राक्षसःअसि","m":"thinking to be Rakshasa"},{"d":"इति","m":"thus"},{"d":"हरयः","m":"monkeys"},{"d":"हरिश्च","m":"and monkeys"},{"d":"असि","m":"thinking to be"},{"d":"इति","m":"thus"},{"d":"राक्षसाः","m":"Rakshasa"},{"d":"समरे","m":"fought"},{"d":"अन्योन्यम्","m":"one another"},{"d":"जघ्नुः","m":"hit ."}]},{"v":4,"dev":"जहिदारयचैहीतिकथंविद्रवसीतिच ।एवंसुतुमुलश्शब्दस्तस्मिंस्तमसिशुश्रुवे कालाःकाञ्चनसन्नाहास्तस्मिंस्तमसिराक्षसाः ।सम्प्रदृश्यन्तशैलेन्द्रादीप्तौषधिवनाइव","trans":"\"Strike\", \"Tear\", \"Why are you running away?\" were the kind of tumultuous echo heard in the darkness of the night. In that darkness the dark complexioned Vanaras and Rakshasas covered with golden armour in the night seemed like shining herbs of the forest in the mountain.","words":[{"d":"जहिदारय","m":"strike"},{"d":"चैहीति","m":"tear"},{"d":"कथं","m":"how"},{"d":"विद्रवसीतिच","m":"why do you run away"},{"d":"एवं","m":"in this manner"},{"d":"सुतुमुलश्शब्द","m":"loud echo"},{"d":"स्तस्मिं","m":"such was"},{"d":"स्तमसि","m":"darkness"},{"d":"शुश्रुवे","m":"heard"},{"d":"तस्मिन्","m":"such was"},{"d":"तमसि","m":"dark complexioned"},{"d":"कालाः","m":"night"},{"d":"काञ्चनसन्नाहाः","m":"covered with golden armour"},{"d":"राक्षसाः","m":"Rakshasa"},{"d":"दीप्तौषधिवनाः","m":"shining like the herbs in the forests"},{"d":"शैलेन्द्राः","m":"mountain"},{"d":"सम्प्रदृश्यन्त","m":"appeared."}]},{"v":5,"dev":"जहिदारयचैहीतिकथंविद्रवसीतिच ।एवंसुतुमुलश्शब्दस्तस्मिंस्तमसिशुश्रुवे कालाःकाञ्चनसन्नाहास्तस्मिंस्तमसिराक्षसाः ।सम्प्रदृश्यन्तशैलेन्द्रादीप्तौषधिवनाइव","trans":"\"Strike\", \"Tear\", \"Why are you running away?\" were the kind of tumultuous echo heard in the darkness of the night. In that darkness the dark complexioned Vanaras and Rakshasas covered with golden armour in the night seemed like shining herbs of the forest in the mountain.","words":[{"d":"जहिदारय","m":"strike"},{"d":"चैहीति","m":"tear"},{"d":"कथं","m":"how"},{"d":"विद्रवसीतिच","m":"why do you run away"},{"d":"एवं","m":"in this manner"},{"d":"सुतुमुलश्शब्द","m":"loud echo"},{"d":"स्तस्मिं","m":"such was"},{"d":"स्तमसि","m":"darkness"},{"d":"शुश्रुवे","m":"heard"},{"d":"तस्मिन्","m":"such was"},{"d":"तमसि","m":"dark complexioned"},{"d":"कालाः","m":"night"},{"d":"काञ्चनसन्नाहाः","m":"covered with golden armour"},{"d":"राक्षसाः","m":"Rakshasa"},{"d":"दीप्तौषधिवनाः","m":"shining like the herbs in the forests"},{"d":"शैलेन्द्राः","m":"mountain"},{"d":"सम्प्रदृश्यन्त","m":"appeared."}]},{"v":6,"dev":"तस्मिंस्तमसिदुष्पारेराक्षसाःक्रोधमूर्छिताः ।परिपेतुर्महावेगाभक्षयन्तःप्लवङ्गमान्","trans":"In that pitch darkness, which was difficult even to move, the Rakshasas overcome by anger and lost senses were wandering devouring the monkeys.","words":[{"d":"दुष्पारे","m":"difficult to penetrate"},{"d":"तस्मिन्","m":"in that"},{"d":"तमसि","m":"darkness"},{"d":"क्रोधमूर्छिता","m":"lost senses overcome by anger"},{"d":"राक्षसाः","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"प्लवङ्गमान्","m":"monkeys"},{"d":"भक्षयन्तः","m":"devouring"},{"d":"महावेगाः","m":"swiftly"},{"d":"परिपेतुः","m":"wandered."}]},{"v":7,"dev":"तेहयान् काञ्चनापीडान् ध्वजांश्चाशीविषोपमान् ।आप्लुत्यदशनैस्तीक्ष्णैर्भीमकोपाव्यदारयन् वानराबलिनोयुद्धेऽक्षोभयन् राक्षसींचमूम् ।","trans":"The mighty strong Vanaras, terribly angry at the Rakshasas sprang up to the sky, and tore with their sharp teeth, the horses of Rakshasas decked with golden ornaments pervading like fire in the battle.","words":[{"d":"भीमकोपाः","m":"terribly angry"},{"d":"बलिनः","m":"mighty strong"},{"d":"तेवानराः","m":"those Vanaras"},{"d":"आप्लुत्य","m":"springing up"},{"d":"तीक्ष्णैः","m":"their sharp"},{"d":"धवनैः","m":"teeth"},{"d":"काञ्चनापीडान्","m":"golden ornaments"},{"d":"हयान्","m":"horses"},{"d":"आशीविषोपमान्","m":"pervading like fire"},{"d":"ध्वजांश्च","m":"of the horses"},{"d":"व्यदारयन्","m":"splitting"},{"d":"युद्धे","m":"in battle"},{"d":"राक्षसीम्","m":"Rakshasa's"},{"d":"अक्षोभयन्","m":"tore to pieces."}]},{"v":8,"dev":"कुञ्जरान् कुञ्जरारोहान् पताकाध्वजिनोरथान् कर्षुश्चददंशुश्चदशनैःक्रोधमूर्छिताः ।","trans":"Having lost senses in fury they dragged the elephants, those mounted upon them, and the chariots decorated with posts and flags and tore them with their teeth.","words":[{"d":"व्यदारयन्","m":"lost sense with anger"},{"d":"कुञ्जरान्","m":"elephants"},{"d":"कुञ्जरारोहान्","m":"mounted on elephants"},{"d":"पताकाध्वजिनः","m":"posts tied with flags"},{"d":"रथान्","m":"chariots"},{"d":"चकर्षुः","m":"dragged them"},{"d":"दशनैः","m":"with teeth"},{"d":"ददंशुश्च","m":"destroyed."}]},{"v":9,"dev":"लक्ष्मणश्चापिरामश्चशरैराशीविषोपमैः दृश्यादृश्यानिरक्षांसिप्रवराणिनिजघ्नतुः ।","trans":"Then Rama as well as Lakshmana with their venomous snakelike arrows killed both visible and invisible principal Rakshasas.","words":[{"d":"रामश्च","m":"Rama as well"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणश्चापि","m":"as Lakshmana also"},{"d":"आशीविषोपमैः","m":"shining like venomous snakes"},{"d":"शरैः","m":"arrows"},{"d":"दृश्यादृश्यानि","m":"visible and invisible"},{"d":"प्रवराणि","m":"principal"},{"d":"रक्षांसि","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"निजघ्नतुः","m":"killed"}]},{"v":10,"dev":"तुरङ्गखुरविध्वस्तंरथनेमिसमुत्थितम् रुरोधकर्णनेत्राणियुध्यतांधरणीरजः ।","trans":"Then the dust rose from the ground pulverised the horses' hooves and crushed by the chariot wheels, filling the ears and eyes of those in war.","words":[{"d":"तुरङ्गखुरविध्वस्तम्","m":"pulverised by the horses hooves"},{"d":"रथनेमिसमुत्थितम्","m":"crushed by the wheels of chariots"},{"d":"धरणीरजः","m":"dust from the ground"},{"d":"युध्यताम्","m":"risen"},{"d":"कर्णनेत्राणि","m":"ears and eyes"},{"d":"रुरोध","m":"filled."}]},{"v":11,"dev":"वर्तमानेतथाघोरेसङ्ग्रामेरोमहर्षणे रुधिरोधामहाघोरानद्यस्तत्रप्रसुस्रुवुः ।","trans":"In that way as the war was going on, and rivers of blood flowing with the terrific noise it made hair stand on end.","words":[{"d":"तथा","m":"like that"},{"d":"घोरे","m":"terrible"},{"d":"रोमहर्षणे","m":"horripilation"},{"d":"सङ्ग्रामे","m":"war"},{"d":"वर्तमाने","m":"moving"},{"d":"रुधिरोधा","m":"river of blood"},{"d":"महाघोराः","m":"terrific"},{"d":"नद्यः","m":"noise"},{"d":"तत्र","m":"there"},{"d":"प्रसुस्रुवुः","m":"flowed."}]},{"v":12,"dev":"ततोभेरीमृदङ्गानांपणवानांचनिस्स्वनः शङ्खवेणुस्वनोन्मिश्रस्सम्भूवाद्भुतोपमः ।","trans":"There arose wonderful sounds of musical instruments, the sounds of kettle drums, wooden drums, mixed with conchs and flutes.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"there"},{"d":"भेरीमृदङ्गानाम्","m":"kettle drums and wooden drums"},{"d":"पणवानांच","m":"musical instrument panava"},{"d":"शङ्खवेणुस्वनोमनिश्रः","m":"sounds of conchs, flutes mixed"},{"d":"अद्भुतोपमः","m":"wonderful"},{"d":"निस्स्वनः","m":"rattling sounds"},{"d":"सम्बभूव","m":"arose."}]},{"v":13,"dev":"हतानांस्तनमानानांराक्षसानांचनिःस्वनः शस्तानांवानराणांचसम्बभूवातिदारुणः ।","trans":"There from the battlefield arose the roaring sounds of wounded and appeased Rakshasas and Vanaras.","words":[{"d":"अत्र","m":"there"},{"d":"स्तनमानानाम्","m":"in the battlefield"},{"d":"हतानाम्","m":"wounded"},{"d":"राक्षसानांच","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"शस्तानाम्","m":"appeased"},{"d":"वानराणांच","m":"and Vanaras"},{"d":"दारुणः","m":"dreadful"},{"d":"निःस्वनः","m":"roaring sounds"},{"d":"सम्बभूव","m":"arose."}]},{"v":14,"dev":"हतैर्वानरवीरैश्चशक्तिशूलपरश्वधैः निहतैःपर्वताकारैराक्षसैःकामरूपिभिः ।शस्त्रपुष्पोपहाराचतत्रासीद्युद्धमेदिनी दुर् ज्ञेयादुर्निवेशाचशोणितास्रावकर्दमा ।","trans":"There with warriors of Vanaras wounded by javelins, tridents and axes, and the Rakshasas of mountain size who could change their form at will, the battlefield was muddy, and wet with blood flowing and difficult to reach.","words":[{"d":"तत्र","m":"there"},{"d":"शस्त्रपुष्पोपहारा","m":"offering of flowers dropped from enemies (from the mountain)"},{"d":"युद्धमेदिनी","m":"on the battlefield"},{"d":"हतैः","m":"killed"},{"d":"वानरवीरैश्च","m":"Vanara warriors also"},{"d":"शक्तिशूलपरश्वधैः","m":"by javelins, tridents and axes"},{"d":"निहतैः","m":"wounded"},{"d":"कामरूपिभिः","m":"who can change their form at will"},{"d":"पर्वताकारैः","m":"of mountain size"},{"d":"राक्षसैः","m":"Rakshasa"},{"d":"शोणितास्रावकर्दमा","m":"wetted by the flow of blood"},{"d":"दुर् ज्ञेया","m":"muddy"},{"d":"दुर्निवेशाच","m":"difficult to reach"},{"d":"आसीत्","m":"remained."}]},{"v":15,"dev":"हतैर्वानरवीरैश्चशक्तिशूलपरश्वधैः निहतैःपर्वताकारैराक्षसैःकामरूपिभिः ।शस्त्रपुष्पोपहाराचतत्रासीद्युद्धमेदिनी दुर् ज्ञेयादुर्निवेशाचशोणितास्रावकर्दमा ।","trans":"There with warriors of Vanaras wounded by javelins, tridents and axes, and the Rakshasas of mountain size who could change their form at will, the battlefield was muddy, and wet with blood flowing and difficult to reach.","words":[{"d":"तत्र","m":"there"},{"d":"शस्त्रपुष्पोपहारा","m":"offering of flowers dropped from enemies (from the mountain)"},{"d":"युद्धमेदिनी","m":"on the battlefield"},{"d":"हतैः","m":"killed"},{"d":"वानरवीरैश्च","m":"Vanara warriors also"},{"d":"शक्तिशूलपरश्वधैः","m":"by javelins, tridents and axes"},{"d":"निहतैः","m":"wounded"},{"d":"कामरूपिभिः","m":"who can change their form at will"},{"d":"पर्वताकारैः","m":"of mountain size"},{"d":"राक्षसैः","m":"Rakshasa"},{"d":"शोणितास्रावकर्दमा","m":"wetted by the flow of blood"},{"d":"दुर् ज्ञेया","m":"muddy"},{"d":"दुर्निवेशाच","m":"difficult to reach"},{"d":"आसीत्","m":"remained."}]},{"v":16,"dev":"साबभूवनिशाघोराहरिराक्षसहारिणी कालरात्रीवभूतानांसर्वेषांदुरतिक्रमा ।","trans":"Like the dreadful night for all beings, difficult to spend, as if it were a dissolution, destructive to Vanaras and Rakshasas.","words":[{"d":"सर्वेषाम्","m":"for all beings"},{"d":"भूतानाम्","m":"beings"},{"d":"दुरतिक्रमा","m":"difficult to pass"},{"d":"कालरात्रीव","m":"like the night of dissolution"},{"d":"सानिशा","m":"that night"},{"d":"घोरा","m":"fierce"},{"d":"हरिराक्षसनाशिनी","m":"destructive to Vanaras and Rakshasas"},{"d":"बभूव","m":"remained."}]},{"v":17,"dev":"ततस्तेराक्षसास्तत्रतस्मिंस्तमसिदारुणे राममेवाभ्यवर्तन्तसम्हृष्टाश्शरवृष्टिभिः ।","trans":"Thereafter in that exceedingly fearsome dark night in the battlefield highly delighted Rakshasas assailed Rama with a rain of arrows.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"thereafter"},{"d":"तत्र","m":"there"},{"d":"परमदारुणे","m":"exceedingly fearsome"},{"d":"तस्मिन् तमसि","m":"in that dark night"},{"d":"तेराक्षसाः","m":"those Rakshasas"},{"d":"सम्हृष्टाः","m":"highly delighted"},{"d":"शरवृष्टिभिः","m":"rain of arrows"},{"d":"राममेव","m":"Rama himself"},{"d":"अभ्यवर्तन्त","m":"assailed."}]},{"v":18,"dev":"तेषामापततांशब्दःक्रुद्धानामपिगर्जताम् उद्वर्तइवसत्त्व, नांसमुद्राणांप्रशुश्रुवे ।","trans":"The thundering noise o